import * as React from 'react'
import { Flex, Heading, Input, SimpleGrid, Box } from '@chakra-ui/react'

const PokeDex = () => (
    <Flex height='100vh' alignItems='center' justifyContent='center'>
        <Flex height='80%' width='80%' background='red.300' p={12} rounded={6}>
            <SimpleGrid columns={2} spacing={1}>
                <Box bg='black' height='80%' width='500px'>PokeDex</Box>
                <Box bg='black' height='80%' width='45%'>My Team</Box>
            </SimpleGrid>
        </Flex>
    </Flex>
)

export default PokeDex
